-- Quebec Resources Ministry Halts St. Lawrence River Oil and Gas Exploration
-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 2010-09-27T16:00:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/quebec-halts-oil-and-natural-gas-exploration-along-the-st-lawrence-river.html
Quebec has halted oil and gas
exploration along the St. Lawrence River, according to a
statement today from the natural resources ministry.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
